messageBody:
I now have news from the BBC:

http://quikscript.sourceforge.net/qs_bbc_top_news.pdf

You will notice that the news stories don't appear as neat as the other
news. I spent both yesterday evening and this evening trying to work
with the mess of BBC, and this is the best I can do.

Paul
